Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:56.15,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}兩人相隔著千年的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:58.81,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}相伴著灰色的調和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:01.22,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}愛和自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:04.13,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}卻遲遲無法相遇
